info: The objective of SDPL-Subprogram II is to support the Government’s efforts to create a business environment that is conducive to economic growth and employment generation. Specifically, Subprogram II will continue to support reform measures for (i) enhancing the policy and regulatory framework, (ii) improving SMEs’ access to finance and land use rights, and (iii) facilitating SMEs’ access to markets by improving industrial and technical standards.
name: SMALL AND MEDIUM ENTERPRISE DEVELOPMENT PROGRAM -SUBPROGRAM II
